[Obviously these comments may be premature subject to the details yet
to be revealed in the Department of Justice documents, but if Bruce
had been knowingly using 2 different Ames strains during his prior
vaccine challenge trials he would have been bonkers to use the same
strains, mixed or separate, in the 2001 letter events (if he were
responsible) knowing what he knew then about contemporary genomic
progress and future possible developments in the molecular
identification of _Bacillus anthracis_. If the letter products came
from his laboratory it would not have been him. The FBI has fingered
the wrong man.

The cause of Stevens' death in Florida was publicly announced and
there was a 24-hour or longer gap before the next batch of letters
was posted and therefore the deed of 2nd posting was patently a
murder attempt on multiple individuals, which was not in his
character. - Mod.MHJ]
